ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 258, Alberta
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER No. 258 in order to (1) declare the natural disaster to be of concern to the federal government; and (2) authorize the provision of financial assistance to Alberta with respect to the interface fires that occurred in Alberta from April 29 to June 22, 2023.
